jspell.modules

Class ModuleAggregator

  • java.lang.Object
    • jspell.modules.ModuleAggregator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module

    public class ModuleAggregator
extends Object
implements Module
    A Module regrouping all other modules and gathering their answers when a search is asked. The DamerauLevenshteinModule is considered the most precise module, with HammingModule and SoundexModule behind.
